title: Brewing recipes
author: DoomsGus
pages:
#- The Brewers' guild              recipies
§0Beers:§r
§0Firstly, some tips. Hops. You can grow them or buy them, I heard that they grow well in the "dead deserts" south of Kannin. There are many varieties of beers known: from a Pale Ale to a Doppel-Bock,§r
#- there are beers for every occasion.
§0The type of beer depends on how long you brew it. Try to avoid barrel aging the beer, it ruins it fast. Better sell or drink it soon! As this was based on the first edition of CivRealms Beers, this only has 8+1 beer§r
#- recipies (+1 because there's an extra). Try adding a 3rd ingredient, it may result in a discovery.
§0Anyway, on with the recipies!§r

#- Pale ale:
